body:
I have a few things I'd like help with;

1) When crafting a chest and key from a gemstone the chest you get is NOT part of snowdown. It's a regular chest. You get no candies and no chance at the poro king loot drop. Is this intended? Did I waste those gemstones? (I have Hextech Annie so I was okay with converting them to chests if I got snowdown stuffs). 

2) Can you get the poro king loot drops in ANY type of chest? Or just the Snowdown Chests ?

replies.body:
Ok then Porocles, thanks.

I was trying to surprise my little brother, but I guess I'll just have to spill the beans today since it's a 1-day thing. {{item:3070}}

Happy Snowdown to you too! {{item:3682}}
